repo.name: cython

commit.message: Benchmarks: Include timings and module sizes for cythonizing Cython.
Use Unix 'time' to benchmark the cythonize runs.

Pre-import Cython before the build to make sure it doesn't try to load partially compiled module sets in older Cython versions.
Run build in parallel to avoid wasting too much time.
Compile also Cython with Limited API when configured for benchmarks.
Print only short DLL module name in sizes report, without platform extension.
Log timings after running a benchmark to give quicker feedback.

title: Benchmarks: Add a benchmark for cythonizing and report the Cython module sizes
